name: COQ AI
description: COQ AI is the companion token to COQ INU, created to take our memecoin ecosystem to the next level. Building on COQ INU’s foundation of art and community, COQ AI is here to grow and evolve. We’re working to make it smarter and better, training it on the amazing art from our meme artists and turning it into a truly creative, useful tool. It’s all about pushing boundaries and making COQ even stronger.
